      "role": "user",
      "content": "everyone says \"it gets better\" but they don't get it. they weren't there when i was crying in the bathroom because of the group chats. it's not just a bad week, it feels like my whole life is ruined. there's no future if everyone looks at me like i'm a joke. how am i supposed to keep going when i just want everything to be quiet and end?",
